# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:18
translate portuguese izzy3_73d87872:

    # "I walk over to where Izzy and her crew are hanging out and see that they're passing around a couple of joints and smoking openly."
    "Dirijo-me para onde a Izzy e o seu grupo estão reunidos e vejo que estão a passar uns charros e a fumar abertamente."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:19
translate portuguese izzy3_b4b71fa1:

    # "The whole place smells like pot as I approach."
    "O sítio todo cheira a erva à medida que me aproximo."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:20
translate portuguese izzy3_94f16c68:

    # gl "Hey, Twig. What's up?"
    gl "Ei, Twig. Tudo bem?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:23
translate portuguese izzy3_fd07d13f:

    # gl "Well come on over, Twig. We just smokin' and chillin' you know?"
    gl "Bem, anda cá, Twig. Estamos só a fumar e a relaxar, percebes?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:25
translate portuguese izzy3_b28ae176:

    # "Izzy looks up at me and one corner of her mouth raises slightly."
    "A Izzy olha para mim e um canto da boca dela levanta-se ligeiramente."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:26
translate portuguese izzy3_a27b96dc:

    # gl "My man. Of course. You might have to contribute somethin' next time though, you know?"
    gl "Meu amigo. Claro. Mas talvez tenhas de contribuir com alguma coisa da próxima vez, sabes?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:29
translate portuguese izzy3_6f7d8c43:

    # "She raises an eye to me."
    "Ela olha para mim de soslaio."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:30
translate portuguese izzy3_cccc2dda:

    # gl "Is that a problem?"
    gl "Isso é um problema?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:31
translate portuguese izzy3_c60076a0:

    # pc "No, I guess not."
    pc "Não, acho que não."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:34
translate portuguese izzy3_1e16ba5c:

    # gl "Here. Get you some."
    gl "Toma. Fuma um pouco."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:41
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_24f5eb86:

    # gl "Yeah boy, get that."
    gl "É isso mesmo, rapaz, fuma isso."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:42
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_23aac278:

    # gl "It's good shit, right?"
    gl "É boa, não é?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:43
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_dad9e95a:

    # "I cough a bit. It's been a while since I smoked, but the quality is surprisingly good. Much better than I expected."
    "Tosso um pouco. Já há algum tempo que não fumava, mas a qualidade é surpreendentemente boa. Muito melhor do que esperava."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:44
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_f83bd81c:

    # pc "Yeah, it's good."
    pc "Sim, é boa."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:45
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_caf1973f:

    # gl "Damn right it is. Locally grown, you know. Best shit in the state."
    gl "Podes crer que é. Cultivada localmente, sabes. A melhor do estado."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:48
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_67e03c26:

    # gl "Getting fucked up always makes me wanna get fucked, you know?"
    gl "Ficar pedrada dá-me sempre vontade de foder, sabes?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:51
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_ebbed377:

    # gl "I bet you could."
    gl "Aposto que sim."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:52
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_8dd9aaab:

    # gl "But Devon would get jealous."
    gl "Mas o Devon ficaria com ciúmes."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:54
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_473d2ea3:

    # gl "A boyfriend? Is this high school?"
    gl "Um namorado? Estamos no liceu?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:55
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_61c896a5:

    # gl "But yes, I'm with Devon."
    gl "Mas sim, estou com o Devon."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:56
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_dc540ae4:

    # "She takes the joint back from me and walks over to Devon."
    "Ela tira-me o charro e dirige-se ao Devon."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:59
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_3ee4a4eb:

    # gl "Technically, he's my man, but we have a sort of open relationship."
    gl "Tecnicamente, ele é o meu homem, mas temos uma espécie de relação aberta."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:60
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_43279dc1:

    # gl "Where he does whatever I want and I do whoever I want."
    gl "Em que ele faz o que eu quiser e eu faço o que quiser."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:61
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_07f4d0f8:

    # gl "Ain't that right baby."
    gl "Não é verdade, querido?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:62
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_818b47b0:

    # "Devon sort of shrugs, taking a deep drag of the joint she slides between his lips."
    "O Devon encolhe os ombros, dando uma tragada profunda no charro que ela desliza entre os lábios dele."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:66
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_c9cd2780:

    # gl "No thanks?"
    gl "Não, obrigado?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:67
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_2b8b122b:

    # gl "I'm offering you free weed and you're telling me no thanks?"
    gl "Estou a oferecer-te erva de graça e dizes-me «não, obrigado»?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:68
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_7f7bd852:

    # gl "You a narc or something? You a cop?"
    gl "És um informador ou algo do género? És polícia?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:69
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_1e908849:

    # pc "No, I just don't smoke."
    pc "Não, só não fumo."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:70
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_8da6b61e:

    # gl "Whatever, Twig. I'm disappointed in you."
    gl "Tanto faz, Twig. Estou desiludida contigo."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:73
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_27a28c0b:

    # "She walks over to Devon and drapes herself over him, sliding the joint between his lips."
    "Ela aproxima-se do Devon e encosta-se a ele, deslizando o charro entre os lábios dele."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:74
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_7c11b8c8:

    # gl "Get you some of that baby."
    gl "Toma um pouco disso, querido."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:75
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_6fd6eefa:

    # "He takes a deep drag and breathes it in with a sigh, a smile creeping over his face."
    "Ele dá uma tragada profunda e inala com um suspiro, um sorriso a surgir-lhe no rosto."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:76
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_dc36117b:

    # "The speaker on the table changes songs and Izzy cocks her head."
    "A coluna na mesa muda de música e a Izzy inclina a cabeça."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:77
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_17789310:

    # gl "Man this song is bumpin! I love this shit."
    gl "Caramba, esta música está a dar que falar! Adoro esta merda."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:78
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_f0694d16:

    # "She turns and starts dancing against Devon, who gets into it as well."
    "Ela vira-se e começa a dançar contra o Devon, que também entra na onda."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:81
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_c676d43f:

    # "She grinds against him, rubbing her juicy ass up and down his crotch."
    "Ela esfrega-se contra ele, esfregando o rabo suculento para cima e para baixo na virilha dele."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:82
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_8e6bf2c6:

    # "I don't know how he can stand it. If I was him, I'd be hard as a rock right now."
    "Não sei como é que ele consegue aguentar. Se eu fosse ele, estaria duro como uma rocha neste momento."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:83
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_277c99a1:

    # "I mean, I kind of am just from watching it."
    "Quer dizer, eu estou meio que assim só de ver."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:85
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_242d472b:

    # "Then there's the chirp of a siren and flashing red and blue lights as headlights illuminate the area we're standing in."
    "Então ouve-se o som de uma sirene e luzes vermelhas e azuis a piscar, enquanto os faróis iluminam a área onde estamos."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:86
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_40384605:

    # mal "Cops!"
    mal "Polícia!"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:87
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_1569f020:

    # moose "I'm out!"
    moose "Vou-me embora!"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:90
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_3068d7c7:

    # "Moose and Mal start running. Devon waits for a moment as Izzy comes up to me."
    "O Moose e o Mal começam a correr. O Devon espera um momento enquanto a Izzy se aproxima de mim."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:91
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_4247ecf9:

    # gl "Better run, Twig!"
    gl "É melhor correres, Twig!"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:93
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_a0a091ac:

    # "She's right. I didn't smoke much, but I'm feeling it. The cops would definitely notice."
    "Ela tem razão. Não fumei muito, mas estou a sentir o efeito. A polícia ia notar, com certeza."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:94
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_81a5df47:

    # "I should run."
    "Devia correr."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:101
translate portuguese smokewithizzy_26da14bf:

    # pc "I'll be okay."
    pc "Vou ficar bem."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:106
translate portuguese izzy5run_c21257c8:

    # "I take off running, looking behind me to see the cops chasing."
    "Começo a correr, olhando para trás para ver a polícia a perseguir-me."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:107
translate portuguese izzy5run_fa42a946:

    # "Izzy and the rest of the gang split off in different directions, but the cops continue chasing me."
    "A Izzy e o resto do grupo separam-se em diferentes direções, mas os polícias continuam a perseguir-me."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:108
translate portuguese izzy5run_dcd48c44:

    # gl "Good luck, Twig! Come back and hang out again sometime!"
    gl "Boa sorte, Twig! Volta para sair connosco outra altura!"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:109
translate portuguese izzy5run_c8db678c:

    # "Izzy's voice trails off as she runs off somewhere."
    "A voz da Izzy vai-se esmorando enquanto ela corre para algum lado."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:110
translate portuguese izzy5run_b40ea09a:

    # "Fortunately the cops that pursue me aren't in the best of shape and after a bit I'm able to outrun them pretty easily."
    "Felizmente, os polícias que me perseguem não estão em grande forma e, passado pouco tempo, consigo ultrapassá-los com bastante facilidade."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:111
translate portuguese izzy5run_5e327114:

    # "It doesn't take long before they give up."
    "Não demora muito até desistirem."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:114
translate portuguese izzy5run_9f09b24a:

    # "I wait a bit, then start making my way back to my car."
    "Espero um pouco e, depois, começo a dirigir-me de volta para o meu carro."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:115
translate portuguese izzy5run_1df6f5ed:

    # "What a wild night. Do they run away from the cops every single night? Seems like they should find a new place to hang out maybe?"
    "Que noite louca. Será que eles fogem da polícia todas as noites? Parece que talvez devessem encontrar um novo sítio para se reunirem?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:116
translate portuguese izzy5run_7001a3d0:

    # "Once I get to my car, I look around to make sure that the cops aren't waiting for me."
    "Assim que chego ao meu carro, olho à minha volta para me certificar de que os polícias não estão à minha espera."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:117
translate portuguese izzy5run_b647d708:

    # "When I'm sure that the coast is clear, I run to the car, get in, and drive away."
    "Quando tenho a certeza de que o caminho está livre, corro para o carro, entro e arranco."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:122
translate portuguese izzy5norun_deb5f235:

    # "Izzy raises her eyebrow at me and then takes off running with the rest of the gang."
    "A Izzy levanta uma sobrancelha para mim e depois sai a correr com o resto do grupo."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:125
translate portuguese izzy5norun_2c82fa04:

    # "I turn and start making my way back towards my car, ready to talk to the police if that's what I have to do."
    "Viro-me e começo a dirigir-me de volta para o meu carro, pronta para falar com a polícia, se for isso que tiver de fazer."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:126
translate portuguese izzy5norun_21f6d686:

    # "But they don't show any interest in me, instead running past me to pursue Izzy's gang."
    "Mas eles não demonstram qualquer interesse em mim, passando por mim a correr para perseguir o grupo da Izzy."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:127
translate portuguese izzy5norun_7bb580de:

    # "I hope they'll be okay. Do they run from the cops like this every night? Seems like they should find a new place to hang out maybe?"
    "Espero que eles fiquem bem. Será que fogem da polícia assim todas as noites? Talvez devessem arranjar um novo sítio para se reunirem?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy3.rpy:128
translate portuguese izzy5norun_cff16f53:

    # "I walk back to my car, get inside, and drive away."
    "Volto para o meu carro, entro e vou-me embora."

